He'll clarify that number, yeah.

11:11.538 --> 11:33.310
did you think that this was being brought actually for texas well it had texas in mind but i think he was buying it for stuff and and that's that's something to do with i mean at the first chance for sale that we had in 1958 fleming would have bought something like 40 percent and he was by far and away

