No, I've no idea.

11:47.670 --> 11:48.791
No, I've no idea.

11:48.811 --> 11:52.995
But I mean, that was pretty much understood that he was acting almost exclusively.

11:53.315 --> 11:56.718
Well, because he had a good relationship with Ransom, I would have thought.

11:56.798 --> 11:59.181
I mean, you mean, do I know any of the scufflepots?

