No, I don't, is the answer.

12:00.402 --> 12:02.824
No, I don't know any of the scufflepots.

12:03.007 --> 12:23.411
any more than, I mean, one knows that among these dealers, in the old days, a dealer would have a cast-iron relationship with certain collectors or librarians.

12:24.292 --> 12:29.098
My father, who died in 1980, and Ted Green of Quaritch, who died about three years ago,

12:29.585 --> 12:39.394
