12:42.537 --> 12:45.660
You never used to have this kind of closeness.

12:45.680 --> 12:53.588
And now, of course, everybody's sharing everything because nobody can afford it anyway to buy it for themselves in a picture sale.

12:54.388 --> 12:59.473
I mean, this is kind of small fly stuff in the book market, but can you imagine...

